729830f-a.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Feldmeyers Lane
729830f-a.text:
4298 (about) Victory Boulevard at the N.E. corner of
Feldmeyers Lane. Beers''s 1874 map shows it to have been the
M. Maybaum house. In 1898 it was owned by John O. Myer. The
vantage point is Victory Boulevard and shows the north side of
Feldmeyers Lane running eastward about 400 feet.
May 19, 1932
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
